{"tid":2159154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[即時討論] 今日4pm 果撚台 - 黎智英 x 林夕 深情對談","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:38:17.000Z","uid":50196,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e72e73e37fee328b1598ca5cff17dbc6d864940f","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"【果燃台直播】不改的約定！黎智英&middot;林夕深情對談<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQd7TWJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQd7TWJ.jpg&h=a79b7f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》在風雨飄搖的日子中，迎來訂閱制1周年，為答謝攜手同行的訂戶，並希望有更緊密聯繫，特別建立升級壹會員尊享的全新互動分享平台「蘋天說地」，頭炮呈獻【不改的約定！黎智英&middot;林夕深情對談】網上FAN享會！8月16日（星期日）下午4時－5時於「果燃台」直播，只限《蘋果》升級壹會員尊享，你更可以在節目中留言，與他們互動。<br />\n<br />\n當黎智英面對最黑暗時刻，林夕多次發文聲援，兩人之間擁有很多從未對外公開的特別情誼。他們約定的對談將於本周日在「果燃台」如期舉行，要來一場深情對談，只限升級壹會員獨家尊享！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">【不改的約定！黎智英&middot;林夕深情對談】網上FAN享會<br />\n日期：2020年8月16日（星期日）<br />\n時間：4:00-5:00pm<br />\n平台：果燃台<br />\n對象：《蘋果動新聞》訂戶（升級壹會員）<br />\n費用：全免</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n問問題，贏$10,000 VIP全年撐蘋果會籍（登記完畢）<br />\n除了在「果燃台」直播收看，我們更會預先選出30位參加者，一齊以網上視像與黎智英和林夕發問及討論，最後他們更會選出問得最好的一位，將可獨得$10,000 VIP全年撐蘋果會籍！參加辦法簡單，只要提交問題，一經選中，會有專人聯絡你講解視像互動詳情。<br />\n* 有關此FAN享會的最新消息，請各位留意電郵、《蘋果動新聞》及【香港蘋果日報】FB專頁 公佈。<br />\n* 被抽中的視像互動參加者將由專人以電郵聯絡。<br />\n* $10,000 VIP全年撐蘋果會籍不能兌換現金，及需在限期內使用。<br />\n* 受條款及細則約束，如有任何爭議，壹傳媒保留最終決定權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgdosgK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgdosgK.jpg&h=0abc5128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbf79ee10401c797a47669aed9ea454f37a716da","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe52d1894e3ce013dbdfd16a84e2013caba9252","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9abb95f96c87963b7fd53d46e0b1f1f6772c5f3","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e582d59644b5e9fc0f37e8b7d4835deef9d28bf","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d46b96ae34c53c0afe838ee65163c1184673469","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22824d2b7f4e28ce6e342ce0ee0663d0bf695cc8","tid":2159154,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befa247fbaae100a4586c36e914d185eed704dc0","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af960a72534b0ff58718084b7d767e3dafffc487","tid":2159154,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"3點"},{"pid":"342455290ca3c49756535b341b87d0ba1a7bc65c","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8514e2381aa4ad4da1dda72b7b1b45f9243a3875","tid":2159154,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj